{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "These seqlets are then clustered into groups and each group is aggregated into a representative motif.",
    "Due to memory and runtime constraints, we used the default value for the maximum number of seqlets per metacluster.",
    "We retrieved expression-predictive motifs (EPMs) using TF-MoDISco that returns both cluster-weighted models and position weight matrices (PWMs).",
    "PWMs were characterised with R statistical language and the package JASPAR2022 calculates various properties of PWMs, such as information content and consensus sequence 24.",
    "In addition, we searched for potential hits between EPMs and already characterised TF binding motifs on the JASPAR plants database (Supplementary Data 4)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "PWMs were characterised with R statistical language and the package JASPAR2022 calculates various properties of PWMs, such as information content and consensus sequence 24."
  ]
}